===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|manga}}

# {{manga}} A [[comic]]; a non-animated cartoon, especially one done in a Japanese style.
# {{manga}} A professionally produced Japanese comic, opposed to [[doujinshi]].

